For over 20 years, we have been helping to improve lives.

As a family owned and operated retail pharmacy who has been in business for over 20 years, our mission is to improve lives and provide the top-notch personalized service that makes a difference for our customers.

At Vital Care Pharmacy, we provide professional prescription services as well as a complete line of health care products, vitamins, and medical supplies. We serve community members
and Adult Day Care Centers.

Why choose us?

Your wellness is our main priority!

Mission & Vision

We strive to provide safe, high-quality patient care in an atmosphere of professionalism, respect, and effective communication. It is our mission to assist communities in obtaining their medications in a timely fashion with little to no stress. By providing medication, supplies and the essentials of good health, our vision is to create a healthier, happier community.

Values

At Vital Care Pharmacy, we genuinely CARE for our patients.

c-compassion

We consider and work to understand how you might be feeling. This compassion is integral to providing the best service. We are all human. We all desire to live a happy, healthy life. And we all need support!

A-Advice

You can count on us for reliable, professional, knowledgeable advice to support healthier, more comfortable lives for our clients.

r-rELIABILITY

We are there when you need us. Not only with our products and services, but with the kind of support, customer service you can count on.

e-excellence

We are driven to consistently achieve the highest standards of excellence with every client, and in every interaction.

We offerFREE delivery

on all orders to Baltimore County, Carroll County, Montgomery County, Harford County, Howard County and beyond!
